---
// 홈페이지 히어로 섹션
---
<section class="banner">
  <div class="hero-aurora" aria-hidden="true">
    <span class="hero-aurora__layer hero-aurora__layer--purple"></span>
    <span class="hero-aurora__layer hero-aurora__layer--navy"></span>
    <span class="hero-aurora__layer hero-aurora__layer--cyan"></span>
  </div>
  <div class="banner__row">

    <div class="banner__container">
      <h1 class="banner__title">대한민국 Physical AI의 대중화를 이끄는 <span class="banner__title-accent">ROBOSEASY</span></h1>
      <div class="banner__subtitle">
        <p class="banner__subtitle-text">로봇이 더 쉽고, 더 가까워지도록.</p>
        <p class="banner__subtitle-text">전국민의 Physical AI 접근성 향상에 기여합니다.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="banner__ctas">
        <a href="/contact" class="banner__cta-primary">문의하기</a>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

  <div class="banner__ticker-inset">
    <div class="client-ticker">
      <div class="client-ticker__track">
        <div class="client-ticker__group">
          <img src="/img/hyundai.png"   alt="현대자동차" class="client-ticker__logo" />
          <img src="/img/hansung.png"   alt="한성대학교" class="client-ticker__logo" />
          <img src="/img/opengraph.png" alt="OpenGraph"  class="client-ticker__logo" />
          <img src="/img/hyundai.png"   alt="현대자동차" class="client-ticker__logo" />
          <img src="/img/hansung.png"   alt="한성대학교" class="client-ticker__logo" />
          <img src="/img/opengraph.png" alt="OpenGraph"  class="client-ticker__logo" />
        </div>
        <div class="client-ticker__group" aria-hidden="true">
          <img src="/img/hyundai.png"   alt="" class="client-ticker__logo" />
          <img src="/img/hansung.png"   alt="" class="client-ticker__logo" />
          <img src="/img/opengraph.png" alt="" class="client-ticker__logo" />
          <img src="/img/hyundai.png"   alt="" class="client-ticker__logo" />
          <img src="/img/hansung.png"   alt="" class="client-ticker__logo" />
          <img src="/img/opengraph.png" alt="" class="client-ticker__logo" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
